99-0591 (La. 4/23/99)

Michael D. JEANE v. ANCO INSULATIONS, INC. No. 99-C-0591. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Jeane, Michael D.; — Plaintiffs); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Office of Workers Compensation District 02 Number 97-03687; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98-1115

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. and KIMBALL, J. would grant on attorneys fees and penalties. JOHNSON, J. not on panel.
